title: Witthaya Nabthong
text: Witthaya Nabthong is a Thai <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who played for <a href="Thailand%20national%20football%20team">Thai internationals</a> in the <a href="2000%20AFC%20Asian%20Cup">2000 AFC Asian Cup</a>.
